Mr Gichunge said bodies of the victims were taken to Kericho County Referral Hospital for preservation before a postmortem is conducted and subsequent release to the relatives.
Police are yet to confirm the number of passengers who were in the Toyota Probox vehicle and the exact number of the injured who were taken to various private hospitals in Kericho town by good Samaritans.
